<node CREATED="1202590799125" ID="Freemind_Link_1419956942" MODIFIED="1202590802437" TEXT="he report found that 32 percent of the organizations never meet with the company&apos;s corporate board or audit committee, and that monthly meetings between the IT and information security teams are three times more likely to occur than meetings between security and corporate officers or business heads. Those security departments that do get face time with the boardroom mostly meet less than once a quarter."/>
</node>
